{"tid":2496660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公務員工會: 宣誓後「篤背脊」文化盛行，過萬人被同事截取社交平台言論投訴","createTime":"2021-04-20T03:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T04:02:27.000Z","uid":5195,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d40a841a9a05fe1f821013ce363356a55f198262","tid":2496660,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"政府指有129名公務員拒絕簽署擁護《基本法》聲明。公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭形容這批公務員「很勇」，犧牲事業去測試政府的底線，相信他們是年資較短的公務員。梁籌庭在本台節目上表示，自從政府要求公務員簽署聲明後，「篤背脊」文化變得盛行，曾經有新入職公務員被同事截取社交平台言論，指控他有政治表述，要交由公務員事務局處理，他得悉有至少過萬宗相關個案。 梁籌庭認為，現時公務員團隊的氣氛很差，人心惶惶，但政府無心解決，質疑局方有心助長「篤背脊」文化。"},{"pid":"a12016214986ef1c48fabc85b16ad09de0d5d49f","tid":2496660,"uid":264387,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:36:03.000Z","msg":"簽得就唔好縮，要做就做最紅最黑果個"},{"pid":"1c28b071a5c6a3d5d617a3cc87ba628bbca0d8ac","tid":2496660,"uid":153811,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"同我估計一樣"},{"pid":"22df024668cba6790e03fb86cea299671a2b490c","tid":2496660,"uid":57,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"簽得就預咗要鬥紅"},{"pid":"cf5df6e1424a727b79952f7b23d0d37cc2af9fe8","tid":2496660,"uid":179729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"人民鬥人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a0f448cce7fdb7e41ebc1e02441a5d58e7fe80","tid":2496660,"uid":24570,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"咁有咩問題先？你宣咗誓就要跟遊戲規則㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130ab340fb9918a9e88d5b1a70a7e8ce5baea0d1","tid":2496660,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:37:10.000Z","msg":"文革係咁啦，你唔鬥人咪俾人鬥死"},{"pid":"38be7d869a703cf914bcf76aa467663d91c09ecd"